# Database Models and Relationships

## Core Models

### User Model
```python
# Located in app/models/users.py
class User:
    id: int (Primary Key)
    supabase_user_id: str (Unique, indexed)  # UUID from Supabase Auth
    email: Optional[str] (indexed, nullable)
    phone: Optional[str] (unique, indexed, nullable)
    full_name: Optional[str]
    date_of_birth: Optional[datetime]
    profile_image_url: Optional[str]
    role: str (default='user')  # 'user', 'agent', 'admin'
    is_active: bool (default=True)
    is_verified: bool (default=False)
    preferences: Optional[dict]
    current_latitude: Optional[float]
    current_longitude: Optional[float]
    notification_settings: Optional[dict]
    privacy_settings: Optional[dict]
    agent_id: Optional[int] (Foreign Key -> agents.id)
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: Optional[datetime]

    # Relationships
    agent: Optional["Agent"]          # Agent profile if role is 'agent'
    owned_properties: List["Property"] # Properties owned by user
    swipes: List["UserSwipe"]         # User's swipe actions
    visits: List["Visit"]             # User's scheduled visits
    bookings: List["Booking"]         # User's bookings
```

### Property Model
```python
# Located in app/models/properties.py
class Property:
    id: int (Primary Key)
    __ts_vector__: Optional[str]  # For full-text search
    title: str
    description: Optional[str]
    property_type: PropertyType  # house, apartment, builder_floor, room
    purpose: PropertyPurpose      # buy, rent, short_stay
    status: PropertyStatus (default='available')

    # Location
    latitude: Optional[float]
    longitude: Optional[float]
    location: Optional[Geography]  # PostGIS geography point
    city: Optional[str]
    state: Optional[str]
    country: str (default='India')
    pincode: Optional[str]
    locality: Optional[str]
    sub_locality: Optional[str]
    landmark: Optional[str]
    full_address: Optional[str]
    area_type: Optional[str]

    # Pricing
    base_price: float
    price_per_sqft: Optional[float]
    monthly_rent: Optional[float]
    daily_rate: Optional[float]
    security_deposit: Optional[float]
    maintenance_charges: Optional[float]

    # Details
    area_sqft: Optional[float]
    bedrooms: Optional[int]
    bathrooms: Optional[int]
    balconies: Optional[int]
    parking_spaces: Optional[int]
    floor_number: Optional[int]
    total_floors: Optional[int]
    age_of_property: Optional[int]
    max_occupancy: Optional[int]
    minimum_stay_days: int (default=1)

    # Features
    features: Optional[dict]
    main_image_url: Optional[str]
    virtual_tour_url: Optional[str]
    tags: Optional[List[str]]
    search_keywords: Optional[str]

    # Owner info
    owner_id: int (Foreign Key -> users.id)
    owner_name: Optional[str]
    owner_contact: Optional[str]
    builder_name: Optional[str]

    # Meta
    is_available: bool (default=True)
    available_from: Optional[datetime]
    calendar_data: Optional[dict]
    view_count: int (default=0)
    like_count: int (default=0)
    interest_count: int (default=0)
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: Optional[datetime]

    # Relationships
    owner: User                          # Property owner
    images: List["PropertyImage"]        # Property images
    property_amenities: List["PropertyAmenity"]  # Property amenities
    swipes: List["UserSwipe"]           # Property swipes
    visits: List["Visit"]               # Property visits
    bookings: List["Booking"]           # Property bookings
```

### Agent Model
```python
# Located in app/models/agents.py
class Agent:
    id: int (Primary Key)
    user_id: int (Foreign Key -> users.id)
    agency_name: Optional[str]
    license_number: Optional[str]
    experience_years: Optional[int]
    specializations: Optional[List[str]]
    service_areas: Optional[List[str]]
    rating: Optional[float]
    total_reviews: int (default=0)
    is_verified: bool (default=False)
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: Optional[datetime]

    # Relationships
    user: User                 # Agent's user account
    visits: List["Visit"]      # Visits scheduled by this agent
```

### Booking Model
```python
# Located in app/models/bookings.py
class Booking:
    id: int (Primary Key)
    user_id: int (Foreign Key -> users.id)
    property_id: int (Foreign Key -> properties.id)
    booking_date: datetime
    check_in_date: Optional[datetime]
    check_out_date: Optional[datetime]
    number_of_guests: int (default=1)
    total_amount: Optional[float]
    status: BookingStatus (default='pending')
    payment_status: PaymentStatus (default='pending')
    special_requests: Optional[str]
    contact_number: Optional[str]
    emergency_contact: Optional[str]
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: Optional[datetime]

    # Relationships
    user: User         # User who made booking
    property: Property # Booked property
```

### Visit Model
```python
# Located in app/models/properties.py (Visit class)
class Visit:
    id: int (Primary Key)
    user_id: int (Foreign Key -> users.id)
    property_id: int (Foreign Key -> properties.id)
    agent_id: Optional[int] (Foreign Key -> agents.id)
    scheduled_date: datetime
    actual_date: Optional[datetime]
    status: VisitStatus (default='scheduled')
    special_requirements: Optional[str]
    visit_notes: Optional[str]
    visitor_feedback: Optional[str]
    interest_level: Optional[str]
    follow_up_required: bool (default=False)
    follow_up_date: Optional[datetime]
    cancellation_reason: Optional[str]
    rescheduled_from: Optional[datetime]
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: Optional[datetime]

    # Relationships
    user: User         # User who scheduled visit
    property: Property # Property to visit
    agent: Optional["Agent"]  # Assigned agent
```

### UserSwipe Model
```python
# Located in app/models/users.py
class UserSwipe:
    id: int (Primary Key)
    user_id: int (Foreign Key -> users.id)
    property_id: int (Foreign Key -> properties.id)
    is_liked: bool
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: Optional[datetime]

    # Relationships
    user: User         # User who swiped
    property: Property # Swiped property

    # Constraints
    # UNIQUE (user_id, property_id) - enforced by index
```

### Amenity Model
```python
# Located in app/models/properties.py
class Amenity:
    id: int (Primary Key)
    title: str (unique)
    icon: Optional[str]
    category: Optional[str]  # e.g., "safety", "recreation", "convenience"
    is_active: bool (default=True)
    created_at: datetime
    updated_at: Optional[datetime]

    # Relationships
    property_amenities: List["PropertyAmenity"]
```

### PropertyAmenity Model (Junction Table)
```python
# Located in app/models/properties.py
class PropertyAmenity:
    id: int (Primary Key)
    property_id: int (Foreign Key -> properties.id)
    amenity_id: int (Foreign Key -> amenities.id)
    created_at: datetime

    # Relationships
    property: Property
    amenity: Amenity

    # Constraints
    # UNIQUE (property_id, amenity_id) - enforced by index
```

## Key Relationships

### One-to-One
- `User -> Agent` (optional, when user.role == 'agent')

### One-to-Many
- `User -> Properties` (as owner)
- `User -> UserSwipes`
- `User -> Visits`
- `User -> Bookings`
- `Property -> PropertyImages`
- `Property -> PropertyAmenities`
- `Property -> UserSwipes`
- `Property -> Visits`
- `Property -> Bookings`
- `Agent -> Visits`

### Many-to-Many
- `Property <-> Amenity` (through PropertyAmenity junction table)

## Database Indexes

### Performance Indexes
- Properties: `property_type`, `purpose`, `is_available`
- Properties: `base_price`
- Properties: PostGIS `location` (GIST index)
- Properties: Full-text search `__ts_vector__`
- Users: `supabase_user_id`, `email`, `phone`
- UserSwipes: `user_id`, `property_id` (unique composite)
- PropertyAmenity: `property_id`, `amenity_id` (unique composite)

